:INFO
Source Your Components
The core of a DIY panel is a Samsung LM301B or LM301H LED strip or board, paired with a \
meanwell driver sized to the wattage you want. A 50W panel for a 2x2 ft space uses \
strips totaling around 50W and a HLG-60H driver set to match. Buy aluminum channel

:PATH
